      "notes": "MOCK of persisting the brief on the content_item (legacy: PATCH /content-items/:id { brief }). In the live orchestrator this brief is instead passed in-memory to caption generation. Replace or remove when wiring the real pipeline."
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Single brief in -> single clean response out\nconst data = $input.first().json;\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    success: true,\n    slot_id: data.slot_id,\n    date: data.date,\n    theme: data.theme,\n    objective: data.objective,\n    brief: data.brief\n  }\n}];\n"
      },
